HEADWORD: Searching
<hw>Search"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Exploring thoroughly;
scrutinizing; penetrating; trying; <as>as, a <ex>searching</ex>
discourse; a <ex>searching</ex> eye</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Piercing,
<xex>searching</xex>, biting, cold.⟦rdquo⟧
